lyTime":"2019-06-29T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母！垃垃港共01！麻煩大家張開雪亮嘅眼睛！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvKoc5u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvKoc5u.png&h=9f58cbb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K65e4ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK65e4ca.png&h=34800640&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"正一食屎狗，情困？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac7a482bc67aab5ee5aaf567799dc6ed5081bf0","tid":1266825,"uid":114701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"見到有個page 好有意思，係一位親子記者寫嘅，借分享俾大家<br />\n<br />\n「<br />\n【亂世兒女  不要用生命打破「共業」的咒】 <br />\n<br />\n#極權統治賤視生命  #我們更要待己慈悲<br />\n<br />\n曾經寫過這一本繪本：《走進生命花園》<br />\n<br />\n當你知道來這一世，是活在槍頭對準自己的極權統治&mdash;&mdash;你還會來這一世修行，做好這份功課？<br />\n<br />\n故事開始，是小朋友坐在自己的島上（第一次看書時，便覺得那是極樂世界）靜觀萬千世界：<br />\n他看到戰爭，便想像長槍可畫成小鳥棲息的樹枝；<br />\n接着，看到肌餓、憂傷、利慾薰心的人、污染的海洋&hellip;&hellip;以及人類寂寞、悲哀有時，流下的眼淚&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n小朋友總用自己的想像，把不完美的世界，看得更積極、美好。然而，看盡塵世醜惡，要他選擇，可願經歷箇中種種？<br />\n<br />\n最後，他選擇「出生」──<br />\n<br />\n各人生命的道場，自有屬於今世需要學習的課題，人與人之間也有不同業力──究竟，我的靈魂緣何有這種選擇？<br />\n<br />\n如何無畏無懼，服膺宇宙法則的力量？<br />\n<br />\n嗯，此書開首，先看到的是Emily Dickinson的詩：<br />\nHope is the thing with feathers, <br />\nThat perches in the soul. <br />\nAnd sings the tune without the words, <br />\nAnd never stops at all.<br />\n<br />\n就是兒童那明澄的心、善良的心，令自己有勇氣去面對無常，再看到希望。<br />\n<br />\n這個世界，每分每秒也在做業；而我們集體的行為、心念，同時有種「共業」：<br />\n<br />\n如果小朋友此刻，感到對世界絕望，想用自己生命控訴極權政府，喚起世人對社會議題的關注⋯⋯懇請再同步想想，自己對香港的愛，也要先對自己慈悲，推己及人，才令很多感絶望的同路人，找到打破「共業」的咒&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我知道可以。這個地方仍有我們的下一代，他們很勇敢，做小靈魂時已經看到自己的生命藍圖，早選擇來到一個正式禮崩樂壞的香港，好好修行做功課&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n不能令這班兒童感到絕望：我們的驅體可以更勇武面對邪惡。<br />\n<br />\n當死諫成為常態，是消弰人心意志，令下一代更絶望⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我們每一個生命，也是齒輪；我們的心念，是動力；<br />\n唯有每個生命先對自己慈悲，那才有良善磁場，令我們的願，可以成功：）<br />\n<br />\n保重自己！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1261090854067357&amp;id=512385395604577&amp;sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1261090854067357%26id%3D512385395604577%26sfnsn%3Dmo&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJoyQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=7f2a70b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1261090854067357&amp;id=512385395604577&amp;sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n豬心記者facebook"},{"pid":"8dd6056fd288349b677358c7e920ce21fa91ece0","tid":1266825,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"757809760607049990fd68618205486ee8009589","tid":1266825,"uid":69960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4edc7d2425c9a7d45523dec4988dc2da1783d607","tid":1266825,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母！垃垃港共01！麻煩大家張開雪亮嘅眼睛！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvKoc5u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvKoc5u.png&h=9f58cbb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K65e4ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK65e4ca.png&h=34800640&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"正一食屎狗，情困？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:58:24.000Z","msg":"情佢老母！寫哂遺書都話情困！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9d3e56ab838683da77de68cfdba6c3ddb6bc79","tid":1266825,"uid":114701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac7a482bc67aab5ee5aaf567799dc6ed5081bf0"